1-Create imigration-department-system database in your localhost mySQL.
2-To change the connection to the database, access the application.properties configuration file that is inside the resources package.
3-Put your Database settings. ie: user, password, database name.
4-To run the application you have to run the main method of the PacketApplication class that is inside the immigration package.

The application is using the Java8 with Spring Framework(Spring Boot, Spring Data JPA) and mySQL database.
I am not sending a Database because it is just run the application that the tables will be created automatically.
You will be able to add all the data using the system.
